            "heading": "The Next Generation of DTF Transfers",
            "paragraph": "<p><strong>VIVID AF</strong> is Ninja’s new standard—upgrading prints from the industry-standard 5-color DTF to 9-color for brighter colors, smoother gradients, and truer matches at no extra cost. Same prices, same settings, same durability—just better prints.</p>",
