        "ai_gen_block_19300fc_Yta7QK": {
          "type": "ai_gen_block_19300fc",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "html_content": "<br><span style=\"font-size:17px; font-weight:900; color:#019AFF;\">Vivid AF Features</span>\n<br><br><br>\n<span style=\"font-size:20px; font-weight:900; color:#000000;; padding-bottom:6px; display:inline-block;\">73% More PANTONE Color Coverage</span><br>\nWe've shattered the color ceiling. Our 9-Color VIVID AF System provides an incredible 73% increase in color coverage compared to standard 5-color DTF. This massive leap moves us from roughly 55% match accuracy to over 95% of the PANTONE Spot Color range, ensuring the most reliable and consistent colors available.<br><br><br>\n<span style=\"font-size:20px; font-weight:900; color:#000000;; padding-bottom:6px; display:inline-block;\">Unmatched Vibrancy &amp; Full Spectrum Detail</span><br>\nSay goodbye to dull and muted colors. The addition of four new channels delivers high saturation and Full Spectrum Detail, resulting in prints that are noticeably sharper, brighter, and truly vivid-giving your designs maximum visual impact.<br><br><br>\n<span style=\"font-size:20px; font-weight:900; color:#000000;; padding-bottom:6px; display:inline-block;\">The \"Advanced Finish\" Advantage</span><br>\nTrue to Design Accuracy: The increased control from the 9-color system means your complex designs, delicate gradients, and tiny details translate to the film with unprecedented precision. The VIVID AF process ensures the finished print is an extremely accurate representation of your original digital artwork.",
            "max_width": 600,
            "vertical_padding": 40,
            "font_size": 16,
            "line_height": 1.6,
            "text_color": "#000000",
            "heading_color": "#000000",
            "link_color": "#019aff",
            "link_hover_color": "#000000",
            "table_header_bg": "#f2f2f2"
          },
          "blocks": {}
        }
